osport.com/football/roberto-mancini_prs12711/person.shtml|publisher=Eurosport|accessdate=20 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[1990\u201391 Serie A|1990\u201391]]\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: [[1984\u201385 Coppa Italia|1984\u201385]], [[1987\u201388 Coppa Italia|1987\u201388]], [[1988\u201389 Coppa Italia|1988\u201389]], [[1993\u201394 Coppa Italia|1993\u201394]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[1991 Supercoppa Italiana|1991]]\n*[[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup|European Cup Winners' Cup]]: [[1989\u201390 European Cup Winners' Cup|1989\u201390]]\n\n'''Lazio'''<ref name=eurosport.com/>\n*Serie A: [[1999\u20132000 Serie A|1999\u20132000]]\n*Coppa Italia: [[1997\u201398 Coppa Italia|1997\u201398]], [[1999\u20132000 Coppa Italia|1999\u20132000]]\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[1998 Supercoppa Italiana|1998]]\n*[[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Cup Winners' Cup|1998\u201399]]\n*[[UEFA Super Cup]]: [[1999 UEFA Super Cup|1999]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Guerin d'Oro]]: [[1987\u201388 Serie A|1987\u201388]], [[1990\u201391 Serie A|1990\u201391]]<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |title=Italy - Footballer of the Year |publisher=RSSSF |accessdate=6 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121013030/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |archivedate=21 January 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[Serie A Footballer of the Year]]: [[1996\u201397 Serie A|1996\u201397]]<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\"/>\n*[[Serie A Italian Footballer of the Year]]: [[1996\u201397 Serie A|1996\u201397]]<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\"/>\n*[[Golden Foot]]: 2017, as [[Golden Foot#Award legends|football legend]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://goldenfoot.com/legends/|title=LEGENDS \u2013 GoldenFoot|publisher=Golden Foot|accessdate=5 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marca.com/en/football/international-football/2017/11/08/5a02d415ca47415c388b4610.html|title=Casillas admits retirement is looming following Golden Foot award|publisher=Marca|date=8 November 2017|accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Orders===\n:[[File:Cavaliere OMRI BAR.svg|left|50px]] 5th Class/Knight: ''[[Italian orders of merit|Cavaliere Ordine al Merito della Repubblica Italiana]]'': 1991<ref name=\"5th class\">{{cite web|url=http://www.quirinale.it/elementi/Onorificenze.aspx?pag=3045&qIdOnorificenza=&cognome=&nome=&daAnno=1800&aAnno=2014&luogoNascita=&testo=&ordinamento=2|title=Onoreficenze|website=quirinale.it|language=Italian|date=30 September 1991|accessdate=19 March 2015}}</ref>\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Manager===\n'''Fiorentina'''<ref name=SW>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/coaches/roberto-mancini/110800/|title=R. Mancini|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=20 December 2015}}</ref>\n*Coppa Italia: [[2000\u201301 Coppa Italia|2000\u201301]]\n\n'''Lazio'''<ref name=SW/>\n*Coppa Italia: [[2003\u201304 Coppa Italia|2003\u201304]]\n\n'''Inter Milan'''<ref name=SW/>\n*Serie A: [[2005\u201306 Serie A|2005\u201306]], [[2006\u201307 Serie A|2006\u201307]], [[2007\u201308 Serie A|2007\u201308]]\n*Coppa Italia: [[2004\u201305 Coppa Italia|2004\u201305]], [[2005\u201306 Coppa Italia|2005\u201306]]\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[2005 Supercoppa Italiana|2005]], [[2006 Supercoppa Italiana|2006]]\n\n'''Manchester City'''\n*[[Premier League]]: [[2011\u201312 Premier League|2011\u201312]]<ref name=PremProfile>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/managers/3916/Roberto-Mancini/overview |title=Manager profile: Roberto Mancini |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=19 September 2018}}</ref>\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[2010\u201311 FA Cup|2010\u201311]]<ref name=SW/>\n*[[FA Community Shield]]: [[2012 FA Community Shield|2012]]<ref name=SW/>\n\n'''Galatasaray'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Turkish Cup]]: [[2013\u201314 Turkish Cup|2013\u201314]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Panchina d'Oro]]: [[2007\u201308 Serie A|2007\u201308]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=775485.html|title=Mancini collects Italian coaching award|publisher=UEFA.com|date=17 November 2008|accessdate=20 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Premier League Manager of the Month]]: [[2010\u201311 Premier League#Monthly awards|December 2010]], [[2011\u201312 Premier League#Monthly awards|October 2011]]<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*[[Italian Football Hall of Fame]]: 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/27-10-2015/hall-of-fame-vialli-mancini-facchetti-ronaldo-herrera-agnelli-tardelli-ferlaino-130676725232.shtml|title=Hall of fame, 10 new entry: con Vialli e Mancini anche Facchetti e Ronaldo|trans-title=Hall of fame, 10 new entries: with Vialli and Mancini also Facchetti and Ronaldo|publisher=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|date=27 October 2015|accessdate=27 October 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Enzo Bearzot Award]]: 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/sport/calcio/2019/04/04/a-mancini-il-premio-bearzot-2019_69b67d27-1eaf-4269-bc8a-abaad455ecef.html|title=A Mancini il premio Bearzot 2019|publisher=Ansa.it|date=4 April 2019|language=italian}}</ref>\n{{col-end}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of English football championship-winning managers]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references group=\"nb\" />\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Instagram|mrmancini10}}\n*[http://www.goal.com/en-gb/people/italy/170/roberto-mancini Roberto Mancini] at Goal.com {{dead link|date=February 2020}}\n*{{Webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302140705/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/Players/Management/Roberto-Mancini |title=Roberto Mancini at Mcfc.co.uk }}\n*{{Soccerbase manager|1709}}\n*[https://www.tuttocalciatori.net/index.php?mod=chp&par=22 Roberto Mancini] at Tuttocalciatori.net {{in lang|it}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ach}}\n{{s-bef|before= [[Carlo Ancelotti]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of FA Cup winning managers|FA Cup<br />Winning Manager]]|years=[[2010\u201311 FA Cup|2010\u201311]]}}\n{{s-aft|after= [[Roberto Di Matteo]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before= [[Alex Ferguson]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Premier League]]<br />Winning Manage