ti]\n* [http://www2.musik.uu.se/UUPart/UUPart.php The Uppsala Partimento Database, UUPart. Compiled and edited by Peter van Tour. Launched 2015, Uppsala.] \n* [http://partimentiscarlatti.blogspot.com/ Partimenti of Alessandro Scarlatti (1660-1725) (D-Hs M/A 251)] \n* [http://bibliotecaestense.beniculturali.it/info/img/mus/i-mo-beu-gamma.l.9.26.pdf Partimenti of Francesco Durante (1684\u20131755) (I-MOe Campori \u03b3 L.9.26)]\n* [http://www.bibliotecamusica.it/cmbm/viewschedatwbca.asp?path=/cmbm/images/ripro/gaspari/EE/EE171/ Partimenti of Francesco Durante (1684\u20131755) (I-Bc EE.171)]\n* [http://www.bibliotecamusica.it/cmbm/viewschedatwbca.asp?path=/cmbm/images/ripro/gaspari/DD/DD219/ Partimenti of Leonardo Leo (1694\u20131744) (I-Bc DD.219)]\n* [http://www.bibliotecamusica.it/cmbm/viewschedatwbca.asp?path=/cmbm/images/ripro/gaspari/DD/DD219/ Partimenti of Pasquale Cafaro (1715\u20131787) (I-Bc DD.219)]\n* [https://daten.digitale-sammlungen.de/~db/0010/bsb00106782/images/ Partimenti of Giuseppe Giacomo Saratelli (1684\u20131762) (D-Mbs Mus. Ms. 1696)]\n* [http://www.internetculturale.it/jmms/objdownload?id=oai%3Awww.internetculturale.sbn.it%2FTeca%3A20%3ANT0000%3AIT%5C%5CICCU%5C%5CMSM%5C%5C0165037&teca=MagTeca%20-%20ICCU&resource=img&mode=all Partimenti of Carlo Cotumacci (1709\u20131785) (I-Nc 34.2.2)]\n* [http://www.internetculturale.it/jmms/iccuviewer/iccu.jsp?id=oai%3Awww.internetculturale.sbn.it%2FTeca%3A20%3ANT0000%3AIT%5C%5CICCU%5C%5CMSM%5C%5C0165040&mode=all&teca=MagTeca+-+ICCU Partimenti of Niccol\u00f2 Zingarelli (1752\u20131837) (I-Nc 34.2.10)]\n\n[[Category:Classical music]]\n[[Category:Musical analysis]]\n[[Category:Musical improvisation]]\n[[Category:Classical period (music)]]\n[[Category:Baroque music]]\n[[Category:18th century in music]]\n[[Category:17th century in music]]\n[[Category:19th century in music]]\n[[Category:18th-century Italian musicians]]\n[[Category:Accompaniment]]\n[[Category:Neapolitan school composers]]\n[[Category:Music theory]